{"tid":118692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇老子無為","createTime":"2017-02-13T08:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T09:18:12.000Z","uid":63071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"397dd6887d6dba0edbf2d1e5c18325611577467c","tid":118692,"uid":63071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"睇道德經睇到頭都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a53f65e9079197c4ddc5d20d24804d4b38c287","tid":118692,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:09:57.000Z","msg":"你試下搵一個叫劉述先嘅人嘅書睇<br />\n佢喺研究老子哲學方面唔錯"},{"pid":"e25e8bbad453cc09af76cea0539c9e491879e8dd","tid":118692,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"當人有慾望點做無為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cb2678899fbb5f53d06ffe4a7ad375dec586a0","tid":118692,"uid":74344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d1c5b63d9dc1247880aa32d92c91ec59a67a54","tid":118692,"uid":74344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚難"},{"pid":"8f4be16b3a39d1b7fd0a4fe7efa046e2812fd4b8","tid":118692,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當人有慾望點做無為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好矛盾，佢又叫你無為，又叫你順應自然。<br />\n<br />\n咁我順從自己的慾望算唔算順應自然先？<br />\n<br />\n慾望係人的天性，咁我順應天性其實係順應自然。<br />\n<br />\n但佢又叫人清心寡慾。"},{"pid":"519709e3218e0265217668fcd61185629e4c6526","tid":118692,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:45:42.000Z","msg":"我都有個疑問:<br />\n<br />\n廿歲年青人應唔應該學習&quot;無為&quot;思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定應該去到中年先學?"},{"pid":"0c08ca484798cea7f391bff87d09df5efaafb153","tid":118692,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當人有慾望點做無為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好矛盾，佢又叫你無為，又叫你順應自然。<br />\n<br />\n咁我順從自己的慾望算唔算順應自然先？<br />\n<br />\n慾望係人的天性，咁我順應天性其實係順應自然。<br />\n<br />\n但佢又叫人清心寡慾。</blockquote><br />\n其實無為會唔會係滿足哂所有慾望先可以做到？但慾望係無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccdaf4b45fd210ecbf766bfc1f41faf7c3029e2","tid":118692,"uid":19978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有個疑問:<br />\n<br />\n廿歲年青人應唔應該學習&quot;無為&quot;思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定應該去到中年先學?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有個說法係人是二十歲之前學儒家就夠，因為無足夠「智慧」和人生閱歷去明白道家的思想"},{"pid":"99346c0d4ad269e1e48edc293f97293a33c1ed31","tid":118692,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當人有慾望點做無為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好矛盾，佢又叫你無為，又叫你順應自然。<br />\n<br />\n咁我順從自己的慾望算唔算順應自然先？<br />\n<br />\n慾望係人的天性，咁我順應天性其實係順應自然。<br />\n<br />\n但佢又叫人清心寡慾。</blockquote><br />\n其實無為會唔會係滿足哂所有慾望先可以做到？但慾望係無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然滿足不了，就不要執著。<br />\n<br />\n學會放下，方能自在。<br />\n<br />\n-究竟算道家定佛家？"}]}